<style>
  esl-share-trigger {
    margin: 10px;
  }
  .demo-trigger-svg-icon {
    width: 50px;
    height: 50px;
  }
</style>

<section>
  <h2>Share</h2>

  <h3>Displays list of share buttons without list attribute</h3>
  <p>Shows all available buttons from config.</p>
  <esl-share></esl-share>
  <hr>

  <h3>Displays list of share buttons with list="all"</h3>
  <p>Shows all available buttons from config.</p>
  <esl-share list="all"></esl-share>
  <hr>

  <h3>Displays list of share buttons with empty list (list="")</h3>
  <p>Shows empty component without buttons.</p>
  <esl-share list=""></esl-share>
  <hr>

  <h3>Displays list of share buttons on nonexistent group</h3>
  <p>Shows empty list when a nonexistent group is specified.</p>
  <esl-share list="group:foo"></esl-share>
  <hr>

  <h3>Displays list of share buttons only existent groups or buttons</h3>
  <p>Shows specified buttons. Displays nothing in the case when specifying the wrong button or group name. (should display LinkedIn, Facebook, Twitter, LinkedIn, Wykop and Copy buttons)</p>
  <esl-share list="linkedin alladin group:alladin group:demo"></esl-share>
  <hr>

  <h3>Displays list of share buttons with repeating buttons</h3>
  <p>Shows component with repeating buttons. (should display 3 buttons LinkedIn)</p>
  <esl-share list="linkedin linkedin linkedin"></esl-share>
  <hr>

  <h3>Displays list of share buttons via incorrect list</h3>
  <p>Shows buttons only with the correct names. (should display only LinkedIn button)</p>
  <esl-share list="twittor  copi group:exsampl linkedin rint"></esl-share>
  <hr>

  <h3>Trigger madness</h3>
  <p>Displays a row of share triggers related to three variations of the popup. The purpose is to check that popup is consistently following the active trigger.</p>
  <p>Hint: the first number is a variant of the share popup, and the second number is a variant of the share attributes.<p>

  <esl-share mode="popup">
    {{ triggerSVGicon('#00BFFF', '1/1') }}
  </esl-share>
  <esl-share mode="popup" list="group:demo">
    {{ triggerSVGicon('#00CED1', '2/1') }}
  </esl-share>
  <esl-share mode="popup" list="group:alternative">
    {{ triggerSVGicon('#8FBC8F', '3/1') }}
  </esl-share>
  <esl-share mode="popup">
    {{ triggerSVGicon('#00BFFF', '1/1') }}
  </esl-share>
  <esl-share mode="popup" {{ shareAttrs2() }}>
    {{ triggerSVGicon('#00BFFF', '1/2') }}
  </esl-share>
  <esl-share mode="popup" list="group:demo">
    {{ triggerSVGicon('#00CED1', '2/1') }}
  </esl-share>
  <esl-share mode="popup" list="group:demo" {{ shareAttrs2() }}>
    {{ triggerSVGicon('#00CED1', '2/2') }}
  </esl-share>
  <esl-share mode="popup" list="group:demo" {{ shareAttrs3() }}>
    {{ triggerSVGicon('#00CED1', '2/3') }}
  </esl-share>
  <esl-share mode="popup" list="group:demo" {{ shareAttrs4() }}>
    {{ triggerSVGicon('#00CED1', '2/4') }}
  </esl-share>
